  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Job Requirement: Degree/Dipoma in Building or Quantity Surveying</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Competent in reading and understanding drawings and perform measurements.</p>\n<p>2. Competent in preparing bills of quantities.</p>\n<p>3. Competent in understanding tender/contract doc/specification/terms of contract.</p>\n<p>4. Competent in analyzing quotation/prices/rates, build-up rates and perform pricing.</p>\n<p>5. Competent in performing contract administration including but not limiting to valuation of payments and variations claims in accordance to contract requirements.</p>\n<p>6. Competent in performing all tender activities necessary for the procurement of new projects.</p>\n<p>7. Competent in working independently as well as a team.</p>\n<p>8. Competent in completing required obligations within stipulated timings and other constraints.</p>",
